i'm querying /json/list again, but also invoking target.gettargets to retrieve all targets. my focus is on determining if /json/list changed with an update to hide iframe targets or if the chat is now categorized as such. previous versions of vs code used to list iframe targets via /json/list. now, the chat might be an iframe i need to find with target.gettargets!

